VERSION 1.0
Additions:
-Added new tool type: blades/knives
-Added new tool: Flint knife
-Added new tool: Iron knife
-Added new progress crafting recipe: flint knapping (to produce flint knife)
-Added new item: Branch

Changes/Tweaks:
-Changed cows to drop at least 1 leather guaranteed.
-Changed leather to render into 2 glue instead of 1 (and 1 cut leather = 1 glue) 
-Changed pork to render into 3 tallow instead of 1
-Brought back beef rendering: beef renders into 1 tallow (why not?)

Fixes:
-Fixed mining charges to drop full blocks of cobble when stone is blasted. Ore chunks are dropped when ore is blasted.